settings_info.votes: choose whether or not Snoo puts votes on posts
settings_info.downvote: choose whether or not Snoo adds downvotes to posts
settings_info.slim nowplaying: shows / hides views and upload date on the nowplaying embed
settings_info.large nowplaying thumbnail: sets the nowplaying thumbnail to the larger, two-message style

error.age_restricted: sorry, but I'm not allowed to play 18+ content since I'm only 6 months old!
error.nothing_found: I wasn't able to find anything. Try something else?
error.no_vc: make sure you're in a voice channel first!
error.not_youtube: that's not a YouTube link, I'm unable to play it!
error.no_content: sorry but I'm unable to understand what the content of that message is.
error.can_not_skip: this is the last song in queue, I have nothing to skip to!
error.can_not_back: this is the first song in queue, I have nothing to go back to!
error.no_url: you did not provide a url and I'm not playing anything so I don't know what to extract!
error.extract: I was unable to extract that url, are you sure it's a proper youtube url?

notifs.loop_start: I'll now loop the current song!
notifs.autoplay_start: I'll do my best to choose a relevant video to play next!
notifs.autoplay_stop: I'll no longer automaticaly play videos!
notifs.back: {} has rewinded to the previous track!
